fields.name: CustomHTTPSConfiguration
fields.description: The configuration specifying how to enable HTTPS

fields.name: CustomHTTPSProvisioningState
fields.description: Provisioning status of Custom Https of the frontendEndpoint.

fields.name: CustomHTTPSProvisioningSubstate
fields.description: Provisioning substate shows the progress of custom HTTPS enabling/disabling process step by step.

fields.name: HostName
fields.description: The host name of the frontendEndpoint. Must be a domain name.

fields.name: SessionAffinityEnabledState
fields.description: Whether to allow session affinity on this host. Valid options are 'Enabled' or 'Disabled'

fields.name: SessionAffinityTtlSeconds
fields.description: UNUSED. This field will be ignored. The TTL to use in seconds for session affinity, if applicable.

fields.name: WebApplicationFirewallPolicyLink
fields.description: Defines the Web Application Firewall policy for each host (if applicable)
